{"about_the_game":"Exosphere is a short but challenging indie game. My take on the punishing climbing game genre. You aim, shoot &amp; bounce your way into the outer layer of the atmosphere using just your mouse. Can you make it to the top?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/extras/promo1.gif?t=1564930507\" /><br><br>The game uses two different views. The eagle-view &amp; the side view. <br>The eagle view is used for observing &amp; navigating through the environment.<br>The side views are primarily used for shooting the ball. Use the mouse to aim &amp; shoot towards your destination.<br>Visit the yellow tiles to save your progress (until you exit the game).<br>If this is your first time playing, watching the tutorial video on the main menu is highly recommended.<br><br>Music by Avaren.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1564930507","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1564930507","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1564930507","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1564930507","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Exosphere is a short but challenging indie game. My take on the punishing climbing game genre. You aim, shoot &amp; bounce your way into the outer layer of the atmosphere using just your mouse. Can you make it to the top?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1048040/extras/promo1.gif?t=1564930507\" /><br><br>The game uses two different views. The eagle-view &amp; the side view. <br>The eagle view is used for observing &amp;